ke]]|GDR}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Tatyana Rodionova (long jumper)|Tatyana Rodionova]]|URS}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Nijol\u0117 Medvedeva]]|URS}}\n|-\n|[[1987 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1987 Indianapolis]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1987 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Heike Drechsler]]|GDR}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Helga Radtke]]|GDR}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Yelena Belevskaya]]|URS}}\n|-\n|[[1989 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1989 Budapest]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1989 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Galina Chistyakova]]|URS}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Marieta Ilcu]]|ROU|1965}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Larysa Berezhna]]|URS}}\n|-\n|[[1991 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1991 Seville]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1991 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Larysa Berezhna]]|URS}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Heike Drechsler]]|GER}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Marieta Ilcu]]|ROU}}\n|-\n|[[1993 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1993 Toronto]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1993 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Marieta Ilcu]]|ROU}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Susen Tiedtke]]|GER}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Inessa Kravets]]|UKR}}\n|-\n|[[1995 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1995 Barcelona]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1995 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Lyudmila Galkina]]|RUS}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Irina Mushailova]]|RUS}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Susen Tiedtke|Susen Tiedtke-Greene]]|GER}}\n|-\n|[[1997 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1997 Paris]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1997 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Fiona May]]|ITA}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Chioma Ajunwa]]|NGR}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Agata Karczmarek]]|POL}}\n|-\n|[[1999 IAAF World Indoor Championships|1999 Maebashi]]<br>{{DetailsLink|1999 IAAF World Indoor Championships \u2013 Women's long jump}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Tatyana Kotova]]|RUS}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Shana Williams]]|USA}}\n|{{flagathlete|[[Iva Pr